Constants.name: Constants
Constants.html:
<gs-row>
    <gs-col width="7">
        <gs-row>
            <gs-title-block padding="10" title="Constants">
                <gs-placeholder id="ph_constantsMainMenu">
                    <gs-snippet snippet="constantsMainMenu"></gs-snippet>
                </gs-placeholder>
            </gs-title-block>
        </gs-row>
    </gs-col>

    <gs-col width="5">
        <gs-placeholder id="ph_selectedConstantsInfo"></gs-placeholder>
    </gs-col>
</gs-row>

InstructionsPerRequest.name: InstructionsPerRequest
InstructionsPerRequest.html:
<gs-title-block title="InstructionsPerRequest" padding="0" margin="0" height="1500"> 
    <gs-chart chartType='hist' group='_type' calc='scriptInstructions' chartPeriod='1d' annotateX='both' query='InstructionsPerRequest'></gs-chart>
</gs-title-block>
